{"title":"妈妈来部队把我看","authors":["张兰生"],"dates":[{"year":1966,"month":8,"day":29}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"妈妈来部队把我看"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"解放军某部战士　张兰生"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妈妈来队把我看，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"说我面貌大改变，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从前瘦小个儿矮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如今脸黑肩又宽。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妈妈的话儿未说完，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我对妈妈开了言："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妈妈呀，个儿长高还不算，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我的思想也在变；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席著作天天学，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我进步快呀干劲添。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妈妈呀，革命熔炉把我炼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"炼就一身英雄胆；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"想起王杰、刘英俊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"何惧千难与万险；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大江大海我能渡，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"险峰峻岭我敢攀！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"知心的话儿有千万，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一时难得说个完；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妈妈听了心高兴，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"两眼笑成一条线。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妈妈拍拍我的肩，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"叮咛一遍又一遍："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要永远听党的话，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"紧握枪杆保江山！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}